snippet.title: Acid Spy - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Acid Spy is a first person stealth action game set in a cyberpunk universe. Infiltrate heavily guarded bases and take down your enemies with skill and finesse. Master the art of quick and deadly stealth to become the acid spy.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/817230/Acid_Spy/

Soundtrack: 
Wolf and Raven - Space Strippers
